Description: =======
        Ganglia
        =======
        
        A library to send metric to Ganglia in python.
        Supports UDP, multicast, group and spoofing.
        
        Installing
        ==========
        
        To install : ::
        
            pip install ganglia
        
        
        Usage
        =====
        
        Sending metric over UDP: ::
        
            ganglia = GMetric("udp://127.0.0.1")
            ganglia.send(
                name='hits',
                units='req/sec',
                type='uint8',
                value=200,
                tmax=60,
                dmax=300,
                group='web'
            )
        
